These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, nurse
1. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Job   | mechanic | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, russian
1. the polish is somewhere to the left of the russian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Nationality   | polish | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, train
1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Transport   | train | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
